PM3AUD.original: ~z~It's a bacon factory out there. Shit.
~z~Alright boys, follow my lead and we might all make it home.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~好了小子们，跟着我来，我们可以一起回去的。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Whatever, at least I'm honest about my habits, Derrick.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~随便啦，至少我吸大麻烟的方法是真的，Derrick。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~This is a matter of national security, immobilize them!
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~This is a matter of national security, immobilize them!

PM3AUD.original: ~z~The National Office of Security Enforcement has really got it in for us.
~z~Lose the cops before we go back to Ma's.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Lose the cops before we go back to Ma's.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I ain't being arrested, Niko. Get rid of these guys.
~z~Niko, these are my two brothers, well two of my brothers, the two that count.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，他们是我的两个哥哥，其中两个哥哥，说得上话的两个。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Patrick, you was such a sweet little boy when I left this city.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Patrick，我刚离开这儿的时候你还是个好孩子。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~That boy's an issue, Niko. Get rid of him.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~That boy's an issue, Niko. Get rid of him.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~which is why he's been married three times already and still won't admit he likes men.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~所以他才会结婚三次还不肯承认自己喜欢男人。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, shit, shit, shit, shit. Michael. Dammit.
~z~Knew I could count on the dumbest member of the group to throw himself into proceedings the most willingly.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我就知道最蠢的组员会最有干劲。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~nothing personal, but don't fuck with my family, or I will fuck with yours.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我不是针对你，但你别给我的家族添乱，否则我要你家好看。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Let's make this clean, boys. No civilian casualties.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~有一点先说清楚，小子们。不要杀害平民。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, there's a road block. Do what you can, Niko boy.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Shit, there's a road block. Do what you can, Niko boy.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I'm not taking that fucking blood money. Them people didn't need to die.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~这票沾满人血的钱老子不要了。他们没必要死的。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~That's a bad omen if ever I saw one. We didn't even get to the damn bank. I'll speak to you soon, Niko.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~That's a bad omen if ever I saw one. We didn't even get to the damn bank. I'll speak to you soon, Niko.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Ireland's not the only thing that's green, dollars are too.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~世上不是只有爱尔兰是绿的，美元也是。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I want Niko and Michael to go down into the vault to get the money while me and my brother handle the crowd control.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko和Michael就冲进金库拿钱，~n~我和我哥负责控制人群。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Hit the needle on the old head there did I, Derrick?
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~往你的古董脑袋上一针见效对吧，Derrick？

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Don't none of you worry about nothing. We're here for the bank's money, it's going to a greater cause.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你们不用害怕，我们只要银行的钱，都是为你们好。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I dunno. Nodding off with a needle sticking outta your arm?
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我不知道。胳膊上插着针管打盹儿？

PM3AUD.original: ~z~The fucks have blocked the road. Try to make it, Niko.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~The fucks have blocked the road. Try to make it, Niko.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Here we are, wait until you're inside to get ballied up.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我们到了，进门了再把头套戴上。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~That's government money they're carrying, don't let them get away!
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~That's government money they're carrying, don't let them get away!

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Derrick, did you sort out the charge for the vault door?
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Derrick，金库大门怎么突破你解决了吗？

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Fuck these people, fuck your cause. That shit's over.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~干他们全家，干你丫的理由。差不多得了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Niko, when the door blows, I want you and Michael to go down into the vault to get the cash.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，门一炸开，你和Michael就进金库拿钱。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~You know nothing about nothing, Patrick. I'm honest about me demons.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你真的是连个屁都不知道，Patrick。~n~我的恶毒可不是开玩笑的。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Had a bit of trouble with that. Couldn't find a pager to rig the blasting cap to.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~那个有点问题。弄不到引爆雷管的接收器。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Packie, take care of Derrick, he's been away.
~z~Yes, yes, it's, uh, nice to meet you.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~记得，记得。那个...很高兴见到你。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Clear the area, please clear the area.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Clear the area, please clear the area.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Christ! This is like being back in the Troubles!
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~天哪！感觉又回到了北爱冲突的时候！

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Anyone tries anything, you put them down hard.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~有人轻举妄动，就直接把他干了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~We told you not to fuck with us!
~z~None of yous is gonna get a medal for playing hero. All you's gonna get is a bullet to the heart.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~都别想逞英雄，谁敢反抗就等着吃枪子儿吧。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Get us and the money out of here, Niko. Fuck.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Get us and the money out of here, Niko. Fuck.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Niko, there ain't no way we're leading all these cops back to the house. Lose 'em.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko, there ain't no way we're leading all these cops back to the house. Lose 'em.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~You're trapped. Lay your weapons down and surrender.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你们被包围了，放下武器，举手投降。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, alright, we can roll with a timer. That's cool.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~行吧行吧，定时器也能用。那样挺好。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~There was no need for a brother and sister to get married, but your parents did that and now you're here.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~兄妹之间也用不着结婚，~n~但是你父母结了，现在才有了你。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Me and Michael are on the civilians, Derrick and Niko are on employees.
~z~I scored a touchdown and won the game. The world is built out of bad ideas, my friend.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我触地得分赢得了比赛。世界终究是由各种坏主意构成的，我的朋友。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~None of you fucking fucks move. Get on the floor.
~z~Had to put the thing on a timer.
~z~I was just saying how I'd do what you said, Packie. No need to get abusive.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我只是说一下我怎么执行而已，Packie。~n~用不着骂我吧。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Get us and the cash back to the house, Niko. Fuck.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Get us and the cash back to the house, Niko. Fuck.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~We ain't going back to me ma's house with all this heat, man. Shake the cops.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~We ain't going back to me ma's house with all this heat, man. Shake the cops.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~This is an emotional moment, I can feel the brotherly love in the air.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~真是感人肺腑，我都能感受到~n~空气中弥漫着的兄弟之爱了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Luis... but this ain't such a good idea bro.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Luis...不过这可不是个好主意，兄弟。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~He's sitting tight now. Paid for his stupidity. Man, I'm jumpy.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~现在他老实了。为他的愚蠢付出了代价。~n~老弟，我有点紧张了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~What you think I been doing all day?
~z~Let's handle this peacefully. We have you surrounded.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我们可以和平解决。你们已经被包围了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~What's that mean? Of course I sorted out the charge.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~这算什么话？我当然想好该怎么突破了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Not going to leave much residue on the notes either so they should be washable.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~也不会在钞票上留下太多残留，钱会比较好洗。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Once the situation has been controlled, Derrick's going to rig the vault door with explosive.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~场面控制住之后，~n~Derrick就用炸药炸开金库大门。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~This is it, boys. Moment of truth.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~就是这儿了，小子们。决战时刻。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Do they really need to send another van load of these guys?
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~他们真有必要再送一车人过来吗？

PM3AUD.original: ~z~So you want to involve him in family business.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你想让他插手我们的家族事务是吧。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I haven't seen combat like this since Belfast.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~贝尔法斯特那次以后我还没见过这样的阵仗。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Me and me brother will hold the pigs back. Get us a car, Niko.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Me and me brother will hold the pigs back. Get us a car, Niko.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Stick to me, boys. We gotta get this cash out of here.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~跟着我，小子们。我们要带着钱出去。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Let's move it people, there's nothing to see here.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Let's move it people, there's nothing to see here.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~You was gone a long time, Derrick. From what I remember, you've changed too.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你走得有点久了，Derrick。~n~你也和我记忆中的你改变了太多。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah? They said catching that pass at my high school championship football game was a "bad idea"
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~是吗？我在高校橄榄球决赛的那次接球也被说是「坏主意」，

PM3AUD.original: ~z~who's so stupid he had to tattoo his name on his arm.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~丫居然白痴到把自己名字文胳膊上。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Michael didn't get lucky, did he? Fucking have-a-go-hero. What was he thinking? He shoulda sat tight.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~是Michael运气不好，是吧？去他妈的英勇就义。~n~什么傻逼路人？趴着又不会死。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~You just gotta hope no one gets killed when they do.
~z~This is the National Office of Security Enforcement - come out now with your hands up.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我们是国家安全办公室。举起手来，乖乖投降。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Niko is a trip, man, I met him through that Puerto Rican coke dealer...
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko是个猛男，老兄。我在波多黎各可卡因贩子那里认识他的...

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Another van load of these guys, God give me strength.
~z~If there is a problem, I'll go.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~要是你们问题很大，我就先走了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~We'll hold off the police. You get us some transport, Niko.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~We'll hold off the police. You get us some transport, Niko.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~cause I broke my leg in thirteen places. But...
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~因为那次搞得我的腿十三处骨折。不过...

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Oh, no offense mister... that ain't good enough.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~哦，并无冒犯，先生...那还远远不够。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Jesus Christ, we didn't get into this for people to die. Shit.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Jesus Christ, we didn't get into this for people to die. Shit.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Never does, Patrick. The best laid plans of mice and men often go awry.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~从来都不一样，Patrick。计划永远赶不上变化。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~What I know is he likes a fight, and he ain't the fucking law.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我知道他喜欢干架，还是个法外狂徒。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~No trouble. I have other ways of making money.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我无所谓，我还有别的法子赚钱。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Niko. You want to leave one of us behind? Get something we're all gonna fit in.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~操，Niko。你是想扔下我们之一吗？找辆我们乘得下的东西。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Me and my brother will watch the kids.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我和我哥会看好这群小鬼的。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Don't need to tell me twice, Packie. I'm ready to go. Pumped, is what I am.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~用不着再跟我说一次，Packie。~n~我已经准备好了。热血沸腾就是我了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~There's no problem. Gerry just likes to think he knows best about everything...
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~没有问题。Gerry就喜欢这种当懂哥的感觉...

PM3AUD.original: ~z~It's some limey name for C4 that Derrick here picked up over there.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~可能是Derrick跟哪个英国佬学的C4叫法。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I guess I'm driving myself back. Bye.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~I guess I'm driving myself back. Bye.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Why're you tellin' them we're brothers, you idiot? That's going to make it hard for them to find us, isn't it?
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你丫说我们是兄弟干嘛，傻逼吗？这不是更容易让我们被抓？

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I coulda been nice to him for once in my fucking life. Kid only wanted to help.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我他妈之前该对他好一点的，这小子只是想帮点忙而已。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Gerald was very clear about the way things is going down, boys.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Gerald制定的流程非常详细，小子们。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~You shouldn't be near here, please move on.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~You shouldn't be near here, please move on.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~-And you remember Michael? St Michael...~n~-Yeah, hey.
~z~Can't wait to see what sort of kick C4 residue is going to give me when I snort up a line of chop though one of them notes.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我都忍不住想见识下~n~沾着C4的钞票卷出来的大麻烟有多爽了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~They don't make things easy for us, do they? Damn bridge is blocked.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~They don't make things easy for us, do they? Damn bridge is blocked.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, well, now I gotta explain to his folks that their son is lying dead on the floor of a bank in Algonquin.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~现在我就得去跟他家里解释说~n~他儿子死在Algonquin一家银行的地板上了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Hey? Yo? I'm a gun club member.
~z~There's been too many casualties already. Don't make this any more difficult.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~伤亡已经太多了。别让事情更加难办。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, this boy's causing us some problems. Take him down.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Shit, this boy's causing us some problems. Take him down.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~when you stop shoving half of Bolivia up your nose every Saturday night!
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~只要你别每周六晚上都把半个玻利维亚的毒品吸到肚！

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Don't bring my parents into this, Packie.
~z~Fucking Frankie, he'd be pissed if he could see us now.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~狗逼Frankie，现在他见着我们不得被气死。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~PE4, I ain't never heard of that.
~z~Now listen people, we're your friends. Me and me brother here, we...
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你们都听好了，我们是你们的朋友。我和我弟弟会...

PM3AUD.original: ~z~He loved you, Packie. He was happy you spoke to him. Didn't matter what you was saying.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~他爱你，Packie。你跟他说话他就很高兴了，你说什么都行。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Nothing like it. Nothing could make me love Francis, though.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~那确实。不过想让我爱上Francis压根没门。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, alright. Do we all know what we're doing? Once the vault door blows,
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~行了行了。各位都搞清楚分工了吗？金库门一炸开，

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Walk in with guns and bombs, walk out with the cash. Simple as that.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Walk in with guns and bombs, walk out with the cash. Simple as that.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Get these guys off our backs, Niko.
~z~Alright boys, it's every man for himself until we get past these guys.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Alright boys, it's every man for himself until we get past these guys.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I'm gonna take these rookies downtown. Are you with me?
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我要把这群菜鸡给干了，你一起吗？

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Tell me that when I've got you home.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~这话留到我送你们到家的时候说吧。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~They got the road blocked. Try to get through it.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~They got the road blocked. Try to get through it.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I'm trying to be honest with these people. We've put them through a lot today.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我只是想对他们诚实点。今天给他们添了够多麻烦了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~You think me, me brother and the money are gonna fit in that thing? Get something bigger.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你觉得这玩意够装我、我弟弟和钱吗？找辆大点的来。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~When your kid is living the life, you gotta expect someone to come through the door and break this sorta news.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~既然孩子过着这种日子，~n~就该想到早晚会有人进来说这种事。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Really Michael? You don't think I know that?

PM3AUD.translated: ~z~噢，你就像那个傻逼埃及艳后...

PM3AUD.original: ~z~You lead, Niko. Me and Derrick are gonna follow you to salvation.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~You lead, Niko. Me and Derrick are gonna follow you to salvation.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~We ain't got time to go back in. Let's move out, boys.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~没时间再下去拿了。撤了吧，小子们。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~There's another damn car load of them.
~z~We lost Michael and Derrick, it ain't worth it.
~z~Niko, you're leading us out of here. Let's go.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko, you're leading us out of here. Let's go.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~You're a good man to have around, Niko. A damn good man.
~z~Fuck you, take the needle out your arm then tell me what to do.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~操你妈！先把你膀子上的针头拔下来，再对我发号施令。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Was I talking to you, you inbred halfwit?
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我有跟你说话吗，近亲繁殖的智障？

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I got enough PE4 here to get through anything they throw at us.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我手头的PE4足以突破任何障碍。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I'm surprised you ain't got three eyes, no balls and a club foot.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你没长成三只眼没有蛋还畸形足我倒是很吃惊。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Jesus, another van load of these aggressive bastards.
~z~Derrick has just returned to the family fold after a good few years in the Old Country,
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Derrick在老家待了很多年，最近才回来的，

PM3AUD.original: ~z~No one needs to die, it's just bad luck when you do.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~没有人需要去死，死了只是运气太差。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~It was meant to be easy, Niko. It was meant to be fun. Shit. See you round.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~明明应该很容易的，Niko。明明应该很快乐的。靠。回头见。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Me and St. Michael here are gonna handle the civilians while Niko and Derrick manage the employees.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我和这位St. Michael控制平民，~n~Niko和Derrick就负责解决职员。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~You can get dosed all you like when Niko gets us back.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko带我们回去以后，你爱怎么打药怎么打药。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~and you're so thick you take orders off my idiot brother Packie...
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~蠢到只能在我的白痴弟弟Packie手下办事...

PM3AUD.original: ~z~We just want to take the bank's money and get out of here.
~z~Shit, before the job even fucking started.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Shit, before the job even fucking started.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Now you've said bloody Ireland, that's gonna narrow the search ain't it?
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~你他妈说了爱尔兰是吧，这不是又把范围缩小了？
~z~干他妈的，又是一群狗逼N.O.O.S.E.的人。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Wrong time, wrong place. I'll see you around.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~时候不对，地方不对。我们回头见。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Maybe we should just talk about the job though?
~z~Eye on the road, Niko. We don't want you to have to break no bad news to our ma.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~好好看路，Niko。~n~我们可不想让你跟妈汇报什么坏消息。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~There's no way we're gonna shake the heat in a cop car, man.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~There's no way we're gonna shake the heat in a cop car, man.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Okay... okay... wait a minute. I got it.
~z~The expression is hit the nail on the head, Packie.
~z~I'll let you tell me what to do,
~z~The PE4 has been moulded and is set to explode in sixty seconds.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~PE4已经装好了，设定在六十秒后引爆。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Don't you speak about my parents like that.
~z~That does not make it any easier to hear. And we aren't safe yet.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~那也没什么区别。~n~我们自己都还没安全呢。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Sure. So, Derrick, you got the charge rigged up to your phone?
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~当然。那Derrick，破门的时候是用你的手机引爆吗？

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Safe to say, what we're using is controllable enough to go through any vault door without incinerating whatever's inside.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~这么说吧，这种炸药可控性强，~n~能够炸穿任何金库大门，还不会损伤里面的东西。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I can think of one reason they needed to get married.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我能想出一条他俩会结婚的原因。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, another car load of fucking cops.
~z~I wasn't just driving you two, the money was in the car as well. Remember that.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我不只是替你俩开车，车里面可还有钱呢。记着点。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Get through these bastards and then rendezvous. Let's go.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Get through these bastards and then rendezvous. Let's go.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Gerry was right about you, Mikey. Your parents must have been twins to produce a kid as dumb as you.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Gerry说你说的是一点没错，Mikey。~n~你爸妈得是龙凤胎才能生出你这么个白痴。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, we're heading to the Southern Algonquin branch of the Bank of Liberty.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，我们要去自由城银行的南Algonquin支行。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, here's how the shit is going down. We're gonna go inside and each take down a security guard.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，我先说下这票的安排。~n~进去以后我们一人解决一个保安。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Use your head, Niko. We ain't gonna be able to lose the pigs in a cop car.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Use your head, Niko. We ain't gonna be able to lose the pigs in a cop car.

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Nothing like a sibling's love, eh Derrick?
~z~Grab as much as you can carry.
~z~All makes sense to me. If you guys can stop arguing for a few minutes then I think we might be okay.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我是明白了。只要你们少吵一会儿架，我们基本就稳了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Every police officer in Algonquin's gotta be here.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~估计Algonquin的所有警察都在这儿了。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Thanks, Niko. You're a damn good man.
~z~I make a point of not talking to the unfortunate victims of brother sister marriages.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我特意不跟那些不幸的德国骨科受害者说话的。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~I ain't having this argument with you, Patrick.
~z~We're nearly done here. Keep calm, people.
~z~I got all the money I could. There's still some in there though.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~能拿的钱我都拿上了。不过里面还剩了些。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~They was so ugly that no one else would have 'em.
~z~We've got a clean line of sight, take 'em down!
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~We've got a clean line of sight, take 'em down!

PM3AUD.original: ~z~We won't forget it, Niko. Here's your cut. I'll tell Gerry you did good. He might give you a call or something.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~我们不会忘的，Niko。这是你的那份。~n~我会告诉Gerry你干得很好的。改天他可能会打电话找你。

PM3AUD.original: ~z~Niko, you gotta take these guys down.
~z~Are you fucking crazy? There's no way we'll lose the cops in a police cruiser.
PM3AUD.translated: ~z~Are you fucking crazy? There's no way we'll lose the cops in a police cruiser.
